Boundaries:
Includes Pump;
Includes Coupling;
Includes Strainer;
Includes sealing system (API or not API);
Includes bulkhead stuffing box (seal);
Includes lubrication system


Exclude Electrical Motor HV/LV, ( except for electro submerged pumps);
Exclude Steam Turbines;
Exclude Diesel Engine;
Exclude Hydraulic system;
Exclude Gearboxes;
Exclude Minimum flow control valve;
Exclude Pressure Relief Device;
Exclude Isolation, purge, vent and drain valves (inspeção do estáticos é bem mais detalhada);
